言うのは、おかしいて゛すか？{6}{f}

words.translation:
I want to study. Do you 
think it's weird for a
Grassrunner to say that? {6}{f}

words.text:
わしは、マイリーの司祭の
ハ゛ラムと申すもの。{6}
